00:38:02.760 --> 00:38:05.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
La mujer que vio Marga con tu marido.

693
00:38:09.400 --> 00:38:10.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Sí?

694
00:38:12.760 --> 00:38:13.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sí.

695
00:38:14.040 --> 00:38:16.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[jadea]

696
00:38:20.920 --> 00:38:23.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
- [solloza]
