702
00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya, sí, supongo.

703
00:38:51.840 --> 00:38:55.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Es que últimamente no...
