710
00:39:18.680 --> 00:39:19.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sí.

711
00:39:20.480 --> 00:39:24.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ya. ¿Y lo has hablado con él

712
00:39:24.160 --> 00:39:25.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
o simplemente...?

713
00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:27.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No.

714
00:39:28.320 --> 00:39:32.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No le he dicho nada
porque... estoy embarazada.

715
00:39:33.480 --> 00:39:35.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Y no quiero que sepa...

716
00:39:35.800 --> 00:39:38.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
