717
00:39:39.720 --> 00:39:40.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Embarazada?

718
00:39:51.160 --> 00:39:52.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Disculpe.

719
00:39:53.040 --> 00:39:54.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Don Críspulo Miranda.

720
00:39:54.320 --> 00:39:56.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Periodista del diario <i>El Sol</i>.

721
00:39:56.200 --> 00:39:59.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Quisiera hablar con la responsable
de las telefonistas.

722
00:39:59.440 --> 00:40:01.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Los vecinos de la calle Hortaleza, 23,

723
00:40:01.440 --> 00:40:03.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
cuyo inmueble sufrió
un incendio en el día de ayer,

724
00:40:04.000 --> 00:40:06.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
