815
00:44:38.240 --> 00:44:39.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Miguel] No, no se trata de eso.

816
00:44:41.160 --> 00:44:44.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Es solo que cuando Francisco
ha dicho en la reunión que el Rotary

817
00:44:44.280 --> 00:44:47.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
