853
00:46:50.480 --> 00:46:51.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Señorita Millán, yo...

854
00:46:51.640 --> 00:46:54.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
