861
00:47:18.200 --> 00:47:19.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Enhorabuena.

862
00:47:21.760 --> 00:47:23.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
