875
00:48:01.520 --> 00:48:02.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aquí solo Sara.

876
00:48:03.120 --> 00:48:05.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Está bien. Sara, yo soy Miguel Pascual.

877
00:48:06.240 --> 00:48:07.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
