893
00:48:57.680 --> 00:48:58.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Muchísimo.

894
00:48:59.640 --> 00:49:03.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
