943
00:51:46.320 --> 00:51:47.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Me equivoqué.

944
00:51:49.640 --> 00:51:51.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Estábamos enfadados, Ángeles.

945
00:51:52.400 --> 00:51:53.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
